data.description: HOME WARRANTY AVAILABLE FROM SELLER. - AGENTS SEE AGENT REMARKS FOR IMPORTANT INCENTIVES.  At $78/sq ft this 5,318 sq ft executive home on 2 acres epitomizes luxury and versatility at a steal of a price.  Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3 baths, the two-story residence has undergone a comprehensive 18-month renovation, resulting in a modern haven for both relaxation and productivity.  The interior showcases a pool table room, a magnificent 20 ft floor-to-ceiling stacked stone fireplace, and a spacious glassed/screened-in porch, creating an ideal blend of comfort and entertainment. The kitchen is equipped with the latest technology, featuring wifi-capable double convection ovens and a state-of-the-art induction glass top range.  Outdoors, a beautiful saltwater pool surrounded by a generous patio invites leisure, while a new 30x30 metal shop/storage building adds practicality to the property. Recent updates include energy-efficient windows and enhancements to the three HVAC units, ensuring a contemporary living experience. The residence is unique in its community water and septic system setup, a rare find in rural properties.  This home is strategically designed for various uses.
